infertile Tudor and Valois families, meaning

00:04:03.949 --> 00:04:08.459
that syphilis may be responsible for many
of those miserably boring dynastic power struggles

00:04:08.459 --> 00:04:12.219
of post-Columbus Europe. Anyway, nothing against
syphilis, but it pales in comparison to the

00:04:12.219 --> 00:04:15.579
devastation wrought by Old World diseases
arriving in the New World.

00:04:15.579 --> 00:04:20.359
But the New World did have one gift for the
